CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 16, 1964, pg. 8, reads: "Cutting Cake - Mr. and Mrs. Frederick Stanford cut their wedding cake, following their marriage on May 9. The bride is the former Mrs. Mary Finks."
TitMainTitle: Groom Frederick Stanford, wearing bow tie and jacket with satin lapels, and bride Mary Finks Stanford wearing tiara and floral dress, posed behind three tiered wedding cake at reception on Mingo Street
